{"tid":900033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【BizStarter】年儲十萬用戶！外賣平台Plum 背水一戰「大裁員」","createTime":"2018-11-13T02:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T16:14:50.000Z","uid":13353,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d7283ddfe453dfe09ec2b21a85c7ec6b2bd08c9e","tid":900033,"uid":13353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:17:52.000Z","msg":"間野竟然仲未執<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【BizStarter】年儲十萬用戶！外賣平台Plum 背水一戰「大裁員」<br />\n<br />\n打工仔搵食艱難，而每日面對最大的搵食問題，相信是食晏！現時外賣平台多的是，但本地初創Plum加入戰場，主打白領食晏時段，推出「外賣集運」平台。平台成立未夠一年，已有逾十萬用戶。你以為這是一個創業成功超勵志小品？事實上，公司早前業務增長放慢，更大規模裁員重組，聯合創辦人張漢樑（Desmond）表示，「真係冇得揀，為公司嘅着想，都一定要做。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181113&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58905797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181113%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58905797&d=53WRbafYR%2FlBXwOwb%2Bn%2BKAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d4d3c7bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181113%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58905797&h=49b78e9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181113&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58905797</a>"},{"pid":"b5ed498cd1cda16dbaa49296f52354ee08e1fe6b","tid":900033,"uid":72495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"Is it good ?"},{"pid":"abd6784aae86294da04e3ad1e0c4edee589c9254","tid":900033,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:37:33.000Z","msg":"mouth marketing 輸梗"},{"pid":"cf424d674a6e81c3876d7f40768923949fea7cfc","tid":900033,"uid":187,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T02:54:09.000Z","msg":"D女幾正"},{"pid":"dfeaec3766a9de7171791c2f24aa06864b337aee","tid":900033,"uid":49643,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T04:19:17.000Z","msg":"依檔野冇諗過食物安全問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"